{
  "name": "DisplayFormat",
  "summary": "<p>更改区域的条件格式或表格样式等操作可导致当前用户界面中的显示内容与 <strong>Range</strong> 对象相应属性中的值不一致。使用 <strong>DisplayFormat</strong> 对象的属性可返回当前用户界面中显示的值。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置在当前用户界面中 G2 单元格边框的粗细为 xlThick ，并显示是否设置成功。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;G2&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Style</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Borders</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Weight</span> = xlThick\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;G2&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">DisplayFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Style</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Borders</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Weight</span> == xlThick)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示在当前用户界面中 D3:D5 单元格文本的字体颜色是否为红色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;D3:D5&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">DisplayFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Font</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span> == <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>))\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>代表关联的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Range/Range .htm#Range.Range\">Range</a></strong> 对象的显示设置。只读。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "AddIndent",
      "summary": "<p>当单元格中的文本对齐方式已设置为等距分布（水平或垂直）时，如果文本会自动缩进，则返回 <strong>True</strong>。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个值，该值指示 ET 是否会在单元格中的文本对齐方式设置为等距分布（水平或垂直）时自动缩进当前用户界面中显示的关联 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Range/Range .htm#Range.Range\">Range</a></strong> 对象的文本。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示 B3 单元格文本对齐方式设置为等距分布（水平或垂直）时，文本是否会自动缩进。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B3&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">DisplayFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AddIndent</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例判断 D5:D10 单元格文本对齐方式为等距分布（水平或垂直）时，文本是否会自动缩进，并通知用户。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;D5:D10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">DisplayFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AddIndent</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;文本会自动缩进&quot;</span>)\n    } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;文本不会自动缩进&quot;</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "any",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Borders",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Borders/Borders .htm#Borders.Borders\">Borders</a></strong> 对象，该对象代表当前用户界面中显示的关联 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Range/Range .htm#Range.Range\">Range</a></strong> 对象的边框。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示 B4 单元格边框在当前调色板中颜色的索引值是否为 xlColorIndexNone 。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B4&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">DisplayFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Borders</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorIndex</span> == xlColorIndexNone)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示第一张工作表中 D6 单元格边框的粗细。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;D6&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">DisplayFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Borders</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Weight</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Borders",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Font",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Font/Font .htm#Font.Font\">Font</a></strong> 对象，该对象代表当前用户界面中显示的关联 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Range/Range .htm#Range.Range\">Range</a></strong> 的字体。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示第一个工作表中 A3 单元格文本的字体大小。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A3&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">DisplayFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Font</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Size</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示 D4 单元格文本是否加粗。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;D4&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">DisplayFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Font</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Bold</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Font",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "FormulaHidden",
      "summary": "<p>如果其公式在工作表受保护时处于隐藏状态，则返回 <strong>True</strong>；如果该区域中有些单元格的 <strong>FormulaHidden</strong> 等于 <strong>True</strong>，而有些单元格的 <strong>FormulaHidden</strong> 等于 <strong>False</strong>，则返回 <strong>Null</strong>。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个值，该值指示当前用户界面中显示的关联 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Range/Range .htm#Range.Range\">Range</a></strong> 对象在工作表受保护时是否会隐藏自己的公式。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示 D3 单元格在工作表受保护时是否隐藏公式。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;D3&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">DisplayFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormulaHidden</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例判断 E5:G5 单元格在工作表受保护时是否会隐藏公式，并通知用户。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;E5:G5&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">DisplayFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormulaHidden</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;工作表受保护时会隐藏公式&quot;</span>)\n    } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;工作表受保护时不会隐藏公式&quot;</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "any",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "HorizontalAlignment",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个值，该值表示当前用户界面中显示的关联 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Range/Range .htm#Range.Range\">Range</a></strong> 对象采用水平对齐方式。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示 E3 单元格的水平对齐方式是否为 xlHAlignGeneral 。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;E3&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">DisplayFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">HorizontalAlignment</span> == xlHAlignGeneral)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断 E3:E6 单元格的水平对齐方式是否为 xlHAlignLeft ，并通知用户。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;E3:E6&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">DisplayFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">HorizontalAlignment</span> == xlHAlignLeft) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;水平对齐方式是xlHAlignLeft&quot;</span>)\n    } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;水平对齐方式不是xlHAlignLeft&quot;</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "any",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "IndentLevel",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个值，该值表示当前用户界面中显示的关联 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Range/Range .htm#Range.Range\">Range</a></strong> 对象的缩进级别。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示 E3 单元格的缩进级别。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;E3&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">DisplayFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">IndentLevel</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断 G5:G10 单元格的缩进级别是否为3，并通知用户。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;G5:G10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">DisplayFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">IndentLevel</span> == <span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;缩进级别为3&quot;</span>)\n    } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;缩进级别不为3&quot;</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "any",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Interior",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Interior/Interior .htm#Interior.Interior\">Interior</a></strong> 对象，该对象代表当前用户界面中显示的关联 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Range/Range .htm#Range.Range\">Range</a></strong> 对象的内部。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示 G3 单元格的内部颜色是否为红色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;G3&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">DisplayFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span> == <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>))\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断 E1:E5 单元格的内部颜色是否为 xlColorIndexNone ，并通知用户。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;E1:E5&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">DisplayFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Interior</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorIndex</span> == xlColorIndexNone) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;内部颜色是xlColorIndexNone&quot;</span>)\n    } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;内部颜色不是xlColorIndexNone&quot;</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Interior",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Locked",
      "summary": "<p>如果该区域已锁定，则返回 <strong>True</strong>；如果在工作表受保护时可以修改该区域，则返回 <strong>False</strong>；如果该区域同时包含锁定和未锁定的单元格，则返回 <strong>Null</strong>。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个值，该值指示当前用户界面中显示的关联 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Range/Range .htm#Range.Range\">Range</a></strong> 对象是否已锁定。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示 G5 单元格是否在用户界面显示时被锁定*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;G5&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">DisplayFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Locked</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断 D5:D10 单元格是否在用户界面显示时被锁定，并通知用户*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;D5:D10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">DisplayFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Locked</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;用户界面显示时被锁定&quot;</span>)\n    } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;用户界面显示时未被锁定&quot;</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "any",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "MergeCells",
      "summary": "<p>如果该区域包含合并单元格，则返回 <strong>True</strong>。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个值，该值指示当前用户界面中显示的关联 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Range/Range .htm#Range.Range\">Range</a></strong> 对象是否包含合并单元格。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示 D5:E5 单元格是否包含合并单元格。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;D5:E5&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">DisplayFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">MergeCells</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断 D7:D10 单元格是否包含合并单元格，并通知用户。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;D7:D10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">DisplayFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">MergeCells</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;包含合并单元格&quot;</span>)\n    } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;未包含合并单元格&quot;</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "any",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "NumberFormat",
